Just dug this one out: Punk Special #6 At the Chelsea Nightclub by The Members

Chelsea Nightclub by The Members
Quick last one before home time. Maybe not really a classic like the rest but a sweet little punky pop gem - and Sound of the Suburbs is a nearly perfect Pleasant Valley Sunday update! And...one of my fave ever TOTP performances by Nicky Tesco...
